0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>計唔到<br />\n多左旅客 外來經濟收益<br />\n就業人口 本地收益<br />\n明顯睇長遠 雖然二千憶真係好貴</blockquote><br />\n冇高鐵啲蝗其實都會黎</blockquote><br />\n用幾百億讓小數人富起來"},{"pid":"adf27b5d4bee45b2375513d4f4e268101f62dcbc","tid":345783,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"成條高鐵都輸曬<br />\n拆左佢就差唔多"},{"pid":"9dbf3376ce3160d12cbaed02d23c07adf2094ab9","tid":345783,"uid":34065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"如果採取梁愛詩炸咗佢的提議, 再將那塊地拍賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61dfa81a374f652e096d99b3b8b39b8a7f42be1","tid":345783,"uid":46527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"政治角度＞生意角度"},{"pid":"f44e3488b9a494ae8703779e91f2e14364f5449f","tid":345783,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"仲未計高鐵站當商場咁樣出租比商店既租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n照計當商業地產項目咁玩會好賺過每人收你幾百蚊車票錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}